      %h2 Rockstar happiness
    .muted When you have reached a certain goal, e.g. get promoted, closed a business deal.  This happiness could be meaningful but it is not long lasting.
  .span4
    .text-center
      = image_tag 'lower_expectation.jpg', size: '150x150'
      %h2 Lowered expectation
    .muted If you lower your expectation, you might not be disappointed.  But this happiness is short-term.

